Package GoNature

Class Report

  • java.lang.Object
    • GoNature.Report
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class Report
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Report represents a report submitted by a user regarding a specific park. Each report contains details such as report ID, sender, park name, report type, and date created. This class provides methods to retrieve and modify report details.
    Author:
    Pier Mbariky, Redan Ganim, Bassel Haddad, Joel Hourany, Asaad Sajim, Nadine Halabi
    See Also:
